    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment accepted. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-threshold factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is offset by the standardized regulatory test protocol (ASTM F1717), multi-laboratory replication, and all quantitative acceptance criteria satisfied. E/uval values for all three QoIs are below 1.96 and percentage differences are below 10%. The FEA ensemble is considered sufficiently credible to support the regulatory submission claim. Note: this package conforms to ProfileMinimal; the hash field is populated and the signature workflow is pending countersignature by the responsible engineer.",
